rpc.datagen
Class DataGenerator

java.lang.Object
  rpc.datagen.DataGenerator

public class DataGenerator
extends java.lang.Object

Data Generator provides methods for instantiating a relational database based on a generative causal model and its parameterization.

                                      java.util.List<java.lang.String> parentQueries)

Parameters:
tableName - the name of the relationship table to populate.
connector - the Connector object specifying how to link together entities.
parentQueries - a list of SQL queries that retrieve parent values if the relationship is contingent on a set of parent variables.

parentUnits - the units that correspond to the precise way in which the parent variables affect this attribute.
